<p><strong>Transfer Student - Less than 24 credits</strong></p>
<p>Students with less than 24 semester or 36 quarter hours completed <em><strong>after high school graduation</strong></em>.</p>
<p>To be considered as a transfer student with less than 24 credits you must meet the&nbsp;admission requirements.</p>
<p><em><strong>To learn about admission requirements visit Step 1:</strong></em></p>
<p><a class="intLink" href="x88703.xml" title="Step 1 - Admission Requirements"><img alt="Step 1 - Admission Requirements" src="Images/Admin_Offices/Admissions/Home%20Page%20Redesign/Steps%20Buttons/Step1_Button.jpg" title="Step 1 - Admission Requirements" /></a>&nbsp;</p>
<p>To learn more about how your credits transfer visit <a href="http://www.byui.edu/admissions/transfer">www.byui.edu/admissions/transfer</a>.</p>
<p>Official college transcripts can be submitted in the following ways:</p>
<ul>
<li>A marked sealed envelope.</li>
<li>Electronically through: Avow, E-Scrip-Safe, or National Clearinghouse. Please have transcripts emailed to transcriptsubmit@byui.edu.</li>
</ul>
<p>*Official college transcripts are not accepted by fax.</p>
<p><strong>Ready to apply? Visit&nbsp;<a href="http://www.besmart.com/" title="BeSmart.com website">BeSmart.com</a> to start your application.</strong></p>]]></IntroCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="CellGroup" label="Cells" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false"><numColumns type="enumeration" values="1 2 3 4 5" label="Select number of cell columns." readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">3</numColumns><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_Cell" Name="CellList" label="Cell List" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="CellComponent" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="Cell" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="CellComponent" Expanded="false"/></xPower></xPower><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_BannerAd" Name="BannerAds" label="Rotating Ads (650x216px required)" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="BannerAdComponent" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="BannerAd" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="BannerAdComponent" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Navigation" StartPage="" MaxDepth="" MaxNodes="" GenerationOrder="down" Navigation="" Query="" Name="DeptEvents" label="Define Your Events Folder" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="QuickLinksGroup" label="Quick Links Group" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinks" label="Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinks" label="Column 2" readonly="false" hi